metadata.description:
LNRZ ON SOUND WK 7

thom.ko may be a web3 rookie, but he's a maestro of sound with a voice of gold. We're honored to introduce him to you all.

A note from Thom himself:

"I just made an almond bundt cake. Orange glaze and everything."

lyrics.text:
You’ve got denser bones than me
I couldn’t take a fall like that
Swept you off your feet
Then I’ll take it all right back
Think that how it works
When you’re bouncing out my life
Things are looking up
Still can’t say the words just right
But I tried to move
And I ended up right here
Saw you left confused
Something I would never dare
But you call my name
And I’m always late I know
Said you’re overlooked
Can we make this up I choked

I know I know
You’re asking why
I always fold
Seems reasonable
It really does
